---
layout: default
title: Talks
---

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Talks</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">Exercises, presentations, and conversations that shaped the future of technology, design, and innovation.</p>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-16">Want me to speak at your event? <a href="mailto:mail@gsferreira.com" class="text-black dark:text-white hover:underline">Get in touch!</a></p>

    {% for talk in talks.all %}
    <div class="mb-24">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">{{ talk.title }}</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 whitespace-pre-wrap">{{ talk.description }}</div>

        <div class="mb-4 text-base font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Presented at</div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            {% for presentation in talk.presentations %}
            <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 p-6 rounded-lg flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4">
                <div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">{{ presentation.name }}</h3>
                        <a href="{{ presentation.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 dark:hover:text-gray-200">
                            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <span>{{ presentation.date | readableDate }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    {% if presentation.recording %}
                    <a href="{{ presentation.recording }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-black dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-black px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm hover:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:bg-gray-200 transition">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"></path>
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                        </svg>
                        Watch video
                    </a>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="bg-black dark:bg-gray-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Think different</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Want to invite me to share my thoughts at your event? Let's make something happen.</p>
        <a href="mailto:mail@gsferreira.com" class="inline-block bg-white text-black px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
</div> 